body.html: Angelica Joy came to us in need of a fresh image to relaunch their jewelry brand. Inspired by Angelica's family roots in Italy, we aimed to capture the magic of the Tuscan region. We developed an icon reminiscent of Italian architecture, harking towards the arch doorways found in quiet little towns. The mark also represents her initial with the strategic placement of the diamond in the center. As a part of this brand refresh, we also developed bespoke cards that would be mailed out with purchases as a keepsake and tactile brand touchpoint.
